# SSH Server

## Install SSH Server

    sudo apt-get install openssh-server

## Install SSH-Client

    sudo apt-get install openssh-client

## Configurig SSH Server
 
File **/etc/ssh/ssh_config**

Enable options

*  ForwardX11 yes

Restart SSH Server after any changes in the config file

## Starting - Stopping SSH Server

    sudo service ssh start
    sudo service ssh restart
    sudo service ssh stop

### Connect to SSH

    ssh host
    ssh userid@host
    ssh -X userid@host

Note: The X-programs must be installed on the server